Simple jabber bot wich uses gloox library.
Dependencies:
* gloox library. On Gentoo, for example, just type "emerge net-libs/gloox", on Ubuntu "apt-get install gloox".
* g++ >= 4.6
Modules can be defined in config file, for example
!module = /bin/bash scripts/module.sh

In conference you can use
!module * arg1 arg2 // some text
It will be translated into command
/bin/bash scripts/module.sh arg1 arg2
and some text will be sent into stdout of your script.
